 OnWSReceive←{
     ⍝ ⍺ ←→ Document
     ⍝ ⍵ ←→ JSON Data Received
     d←⍺
     c←⍵
     c.Event≡'SJSR':c.result ⎕TPUT c.id
     c.Document←d
     e←Elements d
     i←e.id⍳c.CurrentTargetId c.TargetId
     c.(CurrentTarget Target)←(e,0)[i]
     0∊c.(CurrentTarget Target):0
     HandleUnqueuedRequest c:0
     _←c ⎕TPUT d.QueuedThread
     0
 }
